<p>I'm working on a Facebook login for a Parse App, and have added the login element, but would now like to add the FB profile email and name into the database. However, I am unable to do so. How would I be able to insert the username and email of a new user who is using Facebook to register on the app? </p>  <pre><code>$scope.loginFacebook = function() {       Parse.FacebookUtils.logIn("email", {          success: function(user) {           if (!user.existed()) {               FB.api('/me?fields=name,email', function (response) {                   var user = new Parse.User();                   user.set("username", response.username);                   user.set("email", response.email);              });             } else {              alert("You're logged in with Facebook!")              //redirect to dashboard page           }         },          error: function(user, error) {           alert("User cancelled the Facebook login or did not fully authorize.");         }      });       };  </code></pre>